descriptionHtml: Since there are not many Undertale themed mods, I thought of replacing the sounds of the skeletons with Papyrus sound files. You can say it's funny, unfunny, stupid, or annoying. I would not mind that, if you don't want the mod, just don't download it. There is no preview videos of this mod yet thought.
author: GrowlingRobot
